structures with trapped radiation inside high-density peaks,\ncontinue to exist both in PIC and fluid simulations. Though the time evolution\ndoes not exactly match in the two simulations as it does prior to the process\nof wave breaking, the time-dependent features exhibited by the remnant\nstructures are characteristically similar.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Aug 2017 11:23:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-17"}
