ental interlayer\ndistance. In the specific case of graphene, the PBE-D2 functional works very\nwell and can be further improved by adjustment of the parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Aug 2017 14:04:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Aug 2018 15:01:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-22"}
